      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Mesh convergence study performed on the pedicle screw and rod geometry with three refinement levels. Peak von Mises stress and construct stiffness QoIs converged within 2% between the two finest meshes. Final mesh selected on basis of convergence criterion."
