      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Independent review of model setup performed by a second analyst at each participating organization. Boundary conditions, material assignments, and contact definitions verified against the simulation plan prior to execution."
