      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model justified by the pre-yield regime of interest. Contact mechanics represented with penalty formulation; frictionless and frictional variants evaluated. Model form assumptions documented and peer-reviewed."
