      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "N=11 physical constructs tested across two independent laboratories. Sample lot traceability documented. Dimensional inspection confirmed constructs fell within specification tolerances used to define nominal FEA geometry."
