      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed using construct stiffness and yield load as primary QoIs. Ensemble prediction intervals overlap experimental scatter bands for 10 of 11 constructs. Mean absolute percentage error 6.3% for stiffness and 8.1% for yield load across the ensemble."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
